828
00:40:35,110 --> 00:40:36,840
so we could hold our heads high.

829
00:40:40,630 --> 00:40:41,920
After the defeat,

830
00:40:42,190 --> 00:40:44,670
we trusted you to rebuild our city walls

831
00:40:45,400 --> 00:40:46,840
and care for the wounded.

832
00:40:47,320 --> 00:40:48,700
But in the end

833
00:40:50,150 --> 00:40:50,920
We all believed

834
00:40:50,920 --> 00:40:52,840
Di Lin would bring us justice.

835
00:40:57,970 --> 00:41:00,700
We know we can't win against you,

836
00:41:01,430 --> 00:41:03,200
but we're not afraid to die.

837
00:41:03,670 --> 00:41:06,070
We're willing to give everything we have

838
00:41:06,670 --> 00:41:08,600
for the people we swore to protect.

839
00:41:08,840 --> 00:41:10,090
Even if we die,

840
00:41:10,800 --> 00:41:12,280
we'll have no regrets.

841
00:41:19,000 --> 00:41:20,070
I'm sorry.

842
00:41:24,760 --> 00:41:25,590
My Lord...

843
00:41:30,300 --> 00:41:31,380
Lord Si Yilin.

844
00:41:32,990 --> 00:41:34,840
Go quickly, Ding Cheng.

845
00:41:35,200 --> 00:41:37,070
People will be here soon.

846
00:41:38,480 --> 00:41:39,850
Let's go.

847
00:41:41,320 --> 00:41:41,920
My Lord,

848
00:41:44,230 --> 00:41:45,760
you still remember who I am?

849
00:41:47,360 --> 00:41:48,560
Of course I remember.

850
00:41:49,360 --> 00:41:53,420
Ding Cheng from the
12th Company of Payi City,

851
00:41:53,700 --> 00:41:55,970
Xiang Yu from the 15th Company,

852
00:41:56,400 --> 00:41:59,110
and Ming Fei from the 17th Company.

853
00:41:59,450 --> 00:42:00,660
I remember all of you.

854
00:42:01,150 --> 00:42:01,750
My Lord...

855
00:42:03,030 --> 00:42:04,760
Seventy thousand soldiers

856
00:42:05,890 --> 00:42:08,170
stood with me to defend Payi.

857
00:42:09,440 --> 00:42:11,970
But in the end, fewer than
a hundred survived.

858
00:42:12,710 --> 00:42:13,320
My Lord.

859
00:42:13,340 --> 00:42:14,900
You are all warriors.

860
00:42:16,380 --> 00:42:20,500
Laying down your life
for the nation and dying in battle

861
00:42:21,230 --> 00:42:22,960
that's what you're meant to do.

862
00:42:23,310 --> 00:42:26,240
But you never should have
endured such humiliation.

863
00:42:26,520 --> 00:42:27,890
This is my failure.

864
00:42:29,710 --> 00:42:31,550
So I'm willing to take the stab.

865
00:42:37,710 --> 00:42:38,320
My Lord.

866
00:42:42,220 --> 00:42:44,220
Give Di Lin some more time.

867
00:42:44,710 --> 00:42:47,070
He will deliver the justice you deserve.

868
00:42:48,480 --> 00:42:49,110
Go.

869
00:42:49,320 --> 00:42:50,760
Someone's coming. Let's go!

870
00:42:50,760 --> 00:42:51,200
My Lord!

871
00:42:51,200 --> 00:42:51,900
Let's go!
